					<p>&gt; xdebug.file_link_format = "txmt://open?url=file://%f&amp;line=%l"</p>
<p>For widows system there is two way for using textmate style links.<br />
First - use E-texteditor that very young. I dislike it even most of bundles implemented but functionality is very very young.</br><br />
The second is my solution. I create universal wrapper that process such links and start extarnal application (editor). In mmy case i use notepad++ that also use xdebug for debuging php code.</br><br />
Also in future i plan to integrate textmate bundles and scripts in it.</br></p>
