					<p>If anyone is using Macports and having a hard time of it, try using zend_extension_debug=/path/to/xdebug.so instead of the standard zend_extension</p>
<p>It took me 3 hours to figure this out and I only came across this tip thanks to a brilliant page at <a rel="nofollow" href="http://community.activestate.com/forum-topic/php-xdebug-troubleshootin">http://community.activestate.com/forum-topic/php-xdebug-troubleshootin</a></p>
