							Matt Young&nbsp;						</strong>
						<strong>said 
						on Aug 29, 2009:</strong>
					</div>
				</span>
				<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="body">
					<p>I finally got xdebug working on MAMP.</p>
<p>1. Must disable Zend Optimizer. I enable startup error log and see the message indicating Xdebuger is not compitable with it.</p>
<p>2. Must use version 5.2. I initially try 5.3 and it just silently fail!</p>
<p>3. I'm not sure but I think the extension manager must be enabled also.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"></div>
